Since 1989, The Bedroom Shop has served customers in Newmarket, Mississauga, Toronto, Bradford, Vaughan, Barrie, King City, Keswick, Whitby, Stouffville and Orangeville with low prices on Mennonite Furniture, Living Room, Dining Room, Bedroom, Bunk Beds, Kids Furniture and Mattress products and top notch customer service.
